    "faker.word — adjectives, nouns, verbs",
    "faker.seed() — set reproducible seed",
    "faker.setDefaultRefDate() — set reference date for relative dates",
    "fakerDE, fakerFR, fakerZH_CN, ... (70+ locale-specific instances)",
